Node:	zxgesture_pub (Gesture sensor, GestureType is an enumeration for possible gestures)
Input:
	None
Config:
	int16 address
	uint8 gesture { (enum) GestureType }
	
	enum GestureType {
		RIGHT_SWIPE = 0x01,
		LEFT_SWIPE = 0x02,
		NO_GESTURE = 0xFF
	}
Output:
	uint8 gesture
Steps:
	1. Initialization: Send read request to I2C bus manager node
	2. Publish gesture to tpc_gesture  (100Hz)
	